![image](https://github.com/JoseMRodriguezM/AIChatbot/assets/76118394/38a070b3-5b70-41b0-8e1b-a51730b2c4d7)

# Usage:

```console
$ chat [OPTIONS]
```

Writing /bye o /exit you can exit from the app

